items.name: A-major-depressive-disorder-classifcation-framework-based-on-EEG-signals-using-statistical-spectral
items.description: This paper proposes a machine learning framework for MDD diagnosis, which uses different types of EEG-derived features. The features are extracted using statistical, spectral, wavelet, functional connectivity, and nonlinear analysis methods.
